commentTextItems.html: chopped to third man for the win, Pietersen the hero today as he took the game away from Australia today, a win by 3 wickets for England

commentPostTextItems.html: The next game in this great NatWest Series is on Tuesday, England v Giantkillers, Bangladesh starting at 13:30GMT
We hope you will be here then for the commentary as we say good night all
Man of the Match: KP Pietersen

commentTextItems.html: slower ball, short and he pulls, but only 1 run to fine leg
smashed to deep midwicket and it lands well in front of Hogg there
pushed to point and Pietersen almost runs himself out following-up too far

commentPostTextItems.html: We have completed the scheduled play time
